graph TB
    subgraph "OGX K8s Operator"
        Controller["OGXServer Reconciler<br/>(controller-runtime)"]
        Webhook["Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS"]
        KustomizeEngine["Embedded Kustomize Engine<br/>(manifest rendering)"]
        LegacyAdoption["Legacy Adoption System<br/>(v1alpha1 → v1beta1 migration)"]

        Controller -->|renders manifests via| KustomizeEngine
        Controller -->|migrates resources via| LegacyAdoption
    end

    User[User / kubectl] -->|creates/updates| OGXServerCR["OGXServer CR<br/>(ogx.io/v1beta1)"]
    User -->|creates/updates| LegacyCR["LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>(llamastack.io/v1alpha1)"]
    OGXServerCR -->|intercepted by| Webhook
    Webhook -->|validates| OGXServerCR
    OGXServerCR -->|watched by| Controller

    subgraph "Managed Resources (per OGXServer)"
        Deployment["Deployment<br/>(OGX server pods)"]
        Service["Service<br/>(ClusterIP)"]
        NetworkPolicy["NetworkPolicy"]
        PVC["PersistentVolumeClaim"]
        HPA["HorizontalPodAutoscaler"]
        PDB["PodDisruptionBudget"]
        Ingress["Ingress<br/>(optional external access)"]
        ConfigMap["ConfigMap<br/>(config.yaml)"]
        SA["ServiceAccount"]
        RB["RoleBinding<br/>(SCC anyuid)"]
    end

    Controller -->|creates/manages| Deployment
    Controller -->|creates/manages| Service
    Controller -->|creates/manages| NetworkPolicy
    Controller -->|creates/manages| PVC
    Controller -->|creates/manages| HPA
    Controller -->|creates/manages| PDB
    Controller -->|creates/manages| Ingress
    Controller -->|creates/manages| ConfigMap
    Controller -->|creates/manages| SA
    Controller -->|creates/manages| RB

    LegacyCR -->|adopted by| LegacyAdoption

    Controller -->|health checks| OGXPod["OGX Server Pod<br/>8321/TCP"]
    Deployment -->|runs| OGXPod

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI["Kubernetes API Server"]
        CertManager["cert-manager /<br/>OpenShift service-ca"]
        Prometheus["Prometheus<br/>(metrics scrape 8443)"]
    end

    Controller -->|CRUD resources| K8sAPI
    CertManager -->|provisions TLS cert| Webhook
    Prometheus -->|scrapes /metrics| Controller

    subgraph "Remote Providers (from OGX server)"
        vLLM["vLLM"]
        OpenAI["OpenAI API"]
        Azure["Azure OpenAI"]
        Bedrock["AWS Bedrock"]
        VertexAI["Google VertexAI"]
        Watsonx["IBM Watsonx"]
        VectorDBs["PGVector / Milvus / Qdrant"]
        S3["S3 Storage"]
    end

    OGXPod -->|inference| vLLM
    OGXPod -->|inference| OpenAI
    OGXPod -->|inference| Azure
    OGXPod -->|inference| Bedrock
    OGXPod -->|inference| VertexAI
    OGXPod -->|inference| Watsonx
    OGXPod -->|vector I/O| VectorDBs
    OGXPod -->|file storage| S3

